{{#cargo_declare:_table=patches|name=String|date=Date|official=URL}}
Infobox for game-update articles, stored in the Cargo table <code>patches</code> (feeds the patch timeline navbox and the "Latest patch" main-page card).

Canonical patch article layout (see [[Project:Style guide]]):
<pre>
{{Patch
| name     = Patch 1.1 — Invaders of Oakveil
| date     = 2025-04-28
| official = https://playvrising.com/...
| prev     = Patch 1.0
| next     = Patch 1.2
}}
Intro sentence: what the update is and its headline feature.

==Additions==
New content, every entity icon-linked with {{ItemFrame}}.
==Changes==
Balance and system changes: "increased to X from Y" notation.
==Fixes==
==Hotfixes==
Date-stamped sub-entries (e.g. ===1.1.1 — 2025-05-06===).
</pre>
